  "optimization_hints": [
    "Q1: Morsel-driven parallel scan of lineitem with thread-local hash aggregation (4 groups fit in L1, perfect hashing viable). Use AVX2 to vectorize SUM/AVG computation. Columnar storage essential for HDD.",
    "Q3: Join order is critical: filter customer by mktsegment first (reduce to ~375K), then hash-join to orders (25M input), then to lineitem (100M+ input). Use bloom filter on customer.c_custkey to prune lineitem early. Partition join inputs by orderkey hash to enable parallel execution with 32 threads per partition. Sort final 10 results locally.",
